author: cms-l1t-offline
body:
Here is a combo of the RCT unpacker + standard sequence change + DQM updates for L1TRCT and L1TdeRCT.
This PR contains the exact same unpacker as #10220, rebased to 74X.

An identical PR for 75X is #10631
A PR for the subset for 76X that hasn't been merged already
(namely standard sequence + DQM updates)
is #10658

@isobelojalvo, @jingyucms, @mcepeda, you all might be interested in this.
title: RCT unpacker plus DQM 74X
